* ============================================================
* TPS7A4701_10V.lib
* Wrapper para TPS7A4701_TRANS configurado a salida +10 V
*
* Pines del s?mbolo:
* IN   EN   GND   NR   OUT
*
* Configuraci?n ANY-OUT:
* VOUT = 1.4 V + 6.4 V + 1.6 V + 0.4 V + 0.2 V = 10.0 V
* ============================================================

.SUBCKT TPS7A4701_10V IN EN GND NR OUT

* Pin order del modelo original:
* 0P1V 0P2V 0P4V 0P8V 1P6V 3P2V 6P4V1 6P4V2 EN GND NR SENSE IN_0 IN_1 OUT_0 OUT_1

XU1 N0P1 GND GND N0P8 GND N3P2 GND N6P4B EN GND NR OUT IN IN OUT OUT TPS7A4701_TRANS

.ENDS TPS7A4701_10V
